\c 4
\s Imisebenzi yamaLevi
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi lakuAroni isithi:
\v 2 Thathani inani lonke lamadodana kaKohathi avela phakathi kwamadodana kaLevi, ngensendo zawo, ngezindlu zaboyise,
\v 3 kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu, wonke ongena enkonzweni ukwenza umsebenzi wethente lenhlangano\x + 4.23,30,35,39,43,47; 8.24. 1 Lan. 23.3,24,27.\x*.
\v 4 Lo ngumsebenzi wamadodana kaKohathi ethenteni lenhlangano: Izinto ezingcwelengcwele\x + 4.19. Eks. 40.10.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Ekusukeni-ke kwenkamba uAroni lamadodana akhe bazakuza behlise iveyili lesembeso\x + Eks. 26.31. Nani 3.31.\x*, basibekele umtshokotsho wobufakazi ngalo\x + Eks. 25.10,16.\x*,
\v 6 bazabeka phezu kwawo izikhumba zikamantswane\x + Eks. 26.14. Nani 4.8,10,11,12,14.\x*, bendlale phezu kwawo ilembu eliluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka lonke, bafake imijabo yawo\x + Eks. 25.13.\x*.
\v 7 Laphezu kwetafula lokubukisa bazakwendlala ilembu eliluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, babeke phezu kwalo imiganu, lenkezo zempepha, lezitsha, lenkezo zomnikelo wokunathwayo; lesinkwa esihlezi sikhona sizakuba phezu kwalo\x + Eks. 25.23,29,30; 37.16. Levi 24.6,8.\x*.
\v 8 Laphezu kwalezizinto bazakwendlala ilembu elibomvu, balembese ngesembeso sezikhumba zikamantswane, bafake imijabo yalo\x + Eks. 25.28.\x*.
\v 9 Bazathatha-ke ilembu eliluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, bembese uluthi lwesibane sesikhanyiso, lezibane zalo\x + Eks. 25.31,37,38.\x*, lendlawu zalo, lemiganu yalo yomlotha, lezitsha zonke zalo zamafutha abasebenza ngazo kulo.
\v 10 Njalo bazalufaka kanye lezinto zalo zonke esembesweni sezikhumba zikamantswane, bakugaxe egodweni.
\v 11 Laphezu kwelathi legolide bazakwendlala ilembu eliluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka\x + Eks. 30.1,3,5.\x*, balembese ngesembeso sezikhumba zikamantswane, bafake imijabo yalo\x + Eks. 30.1,3,5.\x*.
\v 12 Njalo bazathatha yonke impahla yenkonzo, abakhonza ngayo endlini engcwele, bayifake elenjini eliluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka, bayembese ngesembeso sezikhumba zikamantswane, bayigaxe egodweni.
\v 13 Njalo bazasusa umlotha elathini\x + Eks. 27.1,3,6.\x*, bendlale phezu kwalo ilembu eliyibubende,
\v 14 babeke phezu kwalo zonke izinto zalo abakhonza ngazo kulo, izitsha zokuthwala umlilo, amafologwe enyama, lamafotsholo, lemiganu yokufafaza, zonke izinto zelathi\x + Eks. 27.1,3,6.\x*; bendlale phezu kwalo isembeso sezikhumba zikamantswane, bafake imijabo yalo.
\v 15 Lapho uAroni lamadodana akhe sebeqedile ukwembesa indlu engcwele lempahla zonke zendlu engcwele, ekususweni kwenkamba, emva kwalokho amadodana kaKohathi azakuza ukuthwala\x + 7.9; 10.21. Dute. 31.9; 2 Sam. 6.13.\x*, kodwa kawayikuthinta into engcwele hlezi afe\x + 2 Sam. 6.6,7. 1 Lan. 13.9,10.\x*. Lezizinto zingumthwalo wamadodana kaKohathi, ethenteni lenhlangano.
\p
\v 16 Ubongameli bukaEleyazare indodana kaAroni umpristi buzakuba ngamafutha esibane\x + Eks. 25.6; 27.20. Levi 24.2.\x*, lempepha elephunga elimnandi\x + Eks. 25.6; 31.11. Eks. 30.34.\x*, lomnikelo wokudla njalonjalo\x + Eks. 29.40,41.\x*, lamafutha okugcoba\x + Eks. 30.23; 31.11.\x*; ububonisi ngethabhanekele lonke lakho konke okukilo, endlini engcwele lezitsheni zayo.
\p
\v 17 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi lakuAroni isithi:
\v 18 Lingaqumi insendo zesizwe samaKohathi zisuke phakathi kwamaLevi.
\v 19 Kodwa lokho kwenzeni kuwo, ukuze aphile angafi, ekusondeleni kwawo ezintweni ezingcwelengcwele\x + 4.4.\x*; uAroni lamadodana akhe bazangena, bawamise lowo lalowo emsebenzini wakhe lemthwalweni wakhe;
\v 20 kodwa kawayikungena ukubona\x + Eks. 19.21. 1 Sam. 6.12.\x* lapho izinto ezingcwele zigoqelwa, hlezi afe\x + 1 Kho. 8.8.\x*.
\p
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 22 Thatha inani lonke lamadodana kaGerishoni lawo, ngezindlu zaboyise, ngensendo zawo,
\v 23 kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu langaphezulu kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu uzababala; wonke ongena ukukhonza inkonzo, ukuthi enze umsebenzi ethenteni lenhlangano.
\v 24 Lo ngumsebenzi wensendo zamaGerishoni ukukhonza lemthwalweni;
\v 25 bazathwala-ke\x + 4.25,26; 3.25,26.\x* amakhetheni ethabhanekele, lethente lenhlangano\x + Eks. 26.1-6; 36.8.\x*, isembeso salo\x + Eks. 36.14,19.\x*, lesembeso sezikhumba zikamantswane eziphezu kwalo phezulu\x + Eks. 36.14,19.\x*, lesilenge somnyango wethente lenhlangano,
\v 26 lamakhetheni eguma, lesilenge somnyango wesango leguma eliseduze lethabhanekele njalo eduze lelathi inhlangothi zonke, lentambo zazo, lempahla yonke yenkonzo yabo, lakho konke okwenzelwe bona; basebenze-ke.
\v 27 Njengokulaya kukaAroni lamadodana akhe uzakuba njalo umsebenzi wonke wamadodana amaGerishoni emthwalweni wabo wonke lenkonzweni yabo yonke. Uzawamisa ukugcina wonke umthwalo wabo.
\v 28 Lo ngumsebenzi wensendo zamadodana amaGerishoni ethenteni lenhlangano; ukugcinwa kwawo kuzakuba ngaphansi kwesandla sikaIthamari indodana kaAroni umpristi.
\p
\v 29 Amadodana kaMerari uzawabala ngensendo zawo ngezindlu zaboyise,
\v 30 kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu langaphezulu kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu uzababala, wonke ongena enkonzweni, ukusebenza umsebenzi wethente lenhlangano.
\v 31 Lalokhu yikugcinwa komthwalo wabo, njengokomsebenzi wabo wonke ethenteni lenhlangano\x + 4.31,32; 3.36,37.\x*: Amapulanka ethabhanekele, lemithando yalo, lensika zalo, lezisekelo zalo,
\v 32 lensika zeguma inhlangothi zonke, lezisekelo zazo, lezikhonkwane zazo, lezintambo zazo, lempahla yazo yonke, lomsebenzi wazo wonke. Njalo lizaziqamba ngamabizo impahla abafanele ukuzithwala\x + Eks. 38.21.\x*.
\v 33 Lo ngumsebenzi wensendo zamadodana kaMerari, ngokomsebenzi wonke wawo ethenteni lenhlangano, ngaphansi kwesandla sikaIthamari indodana kaAroni umpristi\x + 4.28.\x*.
\p
\v 34 UMozisi loAroni leziphathamandla zenhlangano basebebala amadodana amaKohathi ngensendo zawo langezindlu zaboyise\x + 4.2.\x*,
\v 35 kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu langaphezulu kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu, wonke ongena enkonzweni, emsebenzini wethente lenhlangano.
\v 36 Lalabo ababalwayo kuwo ngensendo zabo babeyizinkulungwane ezimbili lamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi amahlanu.
\v 37 Laba ngababalwayo bensendo zamaKohathi\x + 4.2.\x*, wonke owasebenza ethenteni lenhlangano, oMozisi loAroni abababalayo, ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* ngesandla sikaMozisi.
\v 38 Lalabo ababalwayo bamadodana kaGerishoni, ngensendo zawo, langezindlu zaboyise,
\v 39 kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu langaphezulu kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu, wonke ongena enkonzweni, emsebenzini ethenteni lenhlangano.
\v 40 Lalabo ababalwayo kuwo ngensendo zabo ngezindlu zaboyise babeyizinkulungwane ezimbili lamakhulu ayisithupha lamatshumi amathathu.
\v 41 Laba ngababalwayo bensendo zamadodana kaGerishoni\x + 4.22.\x*, wonke owasebenza ethenteni lenhlangano, oMozisi loAroni abababalayo ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 42 Lalabo ababalwayo bensendo zamadodana kaMerari, ngensendo zawo, ngezindlu zaboyise,
\v 43 kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu langaphezulu kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu, wonke ongena enkonzweni, emsebenzini wethente lenhlangano.
\v 44 Lalabo ababalwayo kuwo ngensendo zabo babeyizinkulungwane ezintathu lamakhulu amabili.
\v 45 Laba ngababalwayo bensendo zamadodana kaMerari\x + 4.29.\x*, oMozisi loAroni abababalayo, ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* ngesandla sikaMozisi.
\p
\v 46 Bonke ababalwayo, oMozisi loAroni leziphathamandla zakoIsrayeli abababalayo, bamaLevi, ngensendo zabo langezindlu zaboyise,
\v 47 kusukela koleminyaka engamatshumi amathathu langaphezulu kusiya koleminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu, wonke owangena ukusebenza umsebenzi wenkonzo lomsebenzi womthwalo ethenteni lenhlangano,
\v 48 lalabo ababalwayo kubo babeyizinkulungwane eziyisificaminwembili lamakhulu amahlanu lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili.
\v 49 Ngokomlayo weN\nd kosi\nd* bababala, ngesandla sikaMozisi, ngulowo lalowo ngokomsebenzi wakhe langokomthwalo wakhe\x + 4.15,24,31.\x*; ngakho babalwa nguye, njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi\x + 4.1,21,29.\x*.